entries.title_d: This elite ambush squadron must be what happened to Magenta squadron. We pray that you will be able to prevail where they didn't. Avenge the Magenta squadron pilot!
entries.title: Endor system: Defeat the Elite Imperial Ambush patrol.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Fleet Command: < You keep surprising me pilot, I didn't think you would make it out of that alive. Head to these coordinates to help Blue squadron. >
entries.complete: You have survived the Suprise Attack!
